Sankalp is a comprehensive platform aimed at reducing poverty and promoting economic growth by leveraging technology and community collaboration. It connects individuals with financial resources, knowledge, and needs, providing tools for expense management, direct marketplace access, and NGO support. The platform incentivizes collaboration through reward systems and ensures inclusivity with AI-driven chatbots, personalized suggestions and multi-language support. By eliminating intermediaries, enhancing accessibility, and fostering mutual assistance, Sankalp empowers communities to achieve financial self-reliance and drive sustainable development
